#### Likelohood-Ratio-Test ####

# H0: both models equally good
# H1: the larger model is the better one
## LRT 2-states
(-1)*2*mod_tts$minimum-(-1)*2*mod.tort$minimum
qchisq(0.95,2) 
## LRT 3-states
(-1)*2*mod_tts3$minimum-(-1)*2*mod.tort3$minimum 
